view.description: List of all bus routes in Edmonton

columns.name: route_id
columns.description: ID that uniquely identifies a route

columns.name: route_long_name
columns.description: Full name of a route. This name is generally more descriptive than the route_short_name and will often include the route's destination or stop.

columns.name: route type
columns.description: Type of Transportation used on the route. 0 - Tram, Streetcar; 1 - Subway; 2- Rail; 3- Bus; etc...

columns.name: route_url
columns.description: URL of a web page about that particular route

General Information.Purpose: To provide a list of all bus routes in Edmonton for cartographic, analysis and tracking purposes.
